import React, { Component } from 'react'
import { Card_yulduzcha, Swipecentermini, SwipeCon, Swiper_1, Swiper_2, Swiper_3, Swiper_4, Swiper_Card, Swiper_text1, Swiper_text2, Swiper_text3, Swiper_text4, Swipe_card1, Swipe_card2, Swipe_card3, Swipe_card4, Swipe_centertext, Text_min1, Text_min2, Text_min3 } from './Swiper.js'
import Swiper_1img from '../../Assets/Swiper1.png'
import Swiper_2img from '../../Assets/Swiper2.png'
import Swiper_3img from '../../Assets/Swiper3.png'
import Swiper_4img from '../../Assets/Swiper4.png'
import Card_yulduz from '../../Assets/yulduz.png'

export default class Swiper extends Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <SwipeCon>
                <Swipe_centertext>Our Best Product</Swipe_centertext>
                <Swipecentermini>
                    <Text_min1>New Plants</Text_min1>
                    <Text_min2>New Arrivals</Text_min2>
                    <Text_min3>Sale</Text_min3>
                    {/* Card */}
                    <Swiper_Card>
                        <Swipe_card1> <Swiper_1 src={Swiper_1img} /> <Swiper_text1>Outdoor Plant</Swiper_text1> <Card_yulduzcha src={Card_yulduz}/> </Swipe_card1>
                        <Swipe_card2> <Swiper_2 src={Swiper_2img} />  <Swiper_text2>Monstera Plant </Swiper_text2></Swipe_card2>
                        <Swipe_card3> <Swiper_3 src={Swiper_3img} />  <Swiper_text3>Pottel Plant</Swiper_text3>  </Swipe_card3>
                        <Swipe_card4> <Swiper_4 src={Swiper_4img} />  <Swiper_text4>Indoor Plant</Swiper_text4> </Swipe_card4>


                    </Swiper_Card>

                </Swipecentermini>


            </SwipeCon>
        )
    }
}
